des: Welcome to WAME Radio, the go-to destination for classic country music in Statesville, North Carolina! Our station is dedicated to bringing you the timeless sounds of the genre, featuring iconic tracks from legendary artists such as Johnny Cash, Dolly Parton, and Merle Haggard. Whether you're a lifelong fan or just discovering the beauty of classic country, WAME offers a warm and inviting atmosphere for all listeners.
